{"tid":1451132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該大家咪撚再同我走老講一二一二","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:05:26.000Z","uid":129532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"533522779b3eb6c87c50ef14ab95c47a7b6e2ddc","tid":1451132,"uid":129532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:11.000Z","msg":"唔係分化 只係狗衝緊就咪阻住晒<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，小弟發夢係深水埗前線位 <br />\n啲狗冇啦啦話跑 咁咪跑囉 <br />\n<strong>屌</strong> 跑到差唔多轉灣位<br />\n我前面有班攬住膊頭一條人鏈咁係到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一二一二</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一黎又慢 二黎又block左前線走佬位<br />\n大佬呀 你地係咪想前線比人拉<br />\n跑啦！ 屌<br />\n<br />\n仲有聽尖沙咀前線話啲狗衝過黎<br />\n前線話有人用同一招一二一二走<br />\n走走下比疑遲鬼壓低一排人<br />\n結果前線三排訓低左 <br />\n<br />\n大家一二一二呢招係二哥回巢前就做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c34143502b9be8e5b555bfaf7de9daf224c8a6d","tid":1451132,"uid":129532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1e8c5f4ced92113af30bf8d9948cb82d371ee21","tid":1451132,"uid":291068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n順手想講下<br />\n發夢幾次見中後排冇乜經驗嘅人<br />\n一見到遠處有煙/聽到疑似槍聲就panic地尖叫向後跑<br />\n咁好易撞到自己人再人踩人<br />\n有經驗嘅幫幫手 大嗌叫大家冷靜啲 試過有用的"},{"pid":"cbaed61c52fa7eb2b1e55a381399ec9543f6f673","tid":1451132,"uid":129532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:44:33.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4fffa16756e1ebcd4b9ffc67bdf0ac596fcf8506","tid":1451132,"uid":129532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1e8c5f4ced92113af30bf8d9948cb82d371ee21","tid":1451132,"uid":291068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re